1{-# OPTIONS_GHC -Wall #-}
2
3-- | Named function.
4
5module Koshucode.Baala.Overture.Fn
6 ( O.Name,
7   Fn (..),
8   Fn2 (..),
9 ) where
10
11import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Overture.Name.String as O
12
13
14-- ----------------------  Fn
15
16-- | Named function.
17data Fn a b = Fn O.Name (a -> b)
18
19-- | Get function name.
20instance O.GetName (Fn a b) where
21    getName (Fn n _) = n
22
23-- | Show function name.
24instance Show (Fn a b) where
25    show f = "Fn " ++ show (O.getName f)
26
27-- | Equality by function name.
28instance Eq (Fn a b) where
29    f1 == f2 = O.getName f1 == O.getName f2
30
31-- | Ordering by function name.
32instance Ord (Fn a b) where
33    compare f1 f2 = compare (O.getName f1) (O.getName f2)
34
35
36-- ----------------------  Fn2
37
38-- | Two-argument named function.
39data Fn2 a b c = Fn2 O.Name (a -> b -> c)
40
41-- | Get function name.
42instance O.GetName (Fn2 a b c) where
43    getName (Fn2 n _) = n
44
45-- | Show function name.
46instance Show (Fn2 a b c) where
47    show f = "Fn2 " ++ show (O.getName f)
48
49-- | Equality by function name.
50instance Eq (Fn2 a b c) where
51    f1 == f2 = O.getName f1 == O.getName f2
52
53-- | Ordering by function name.
54instance Ord (Fn2 a b c) where
55    compare f1 f2 = compare (O.getName f1) (O.getName f2)
